title: Stossel.2014.07.24.Bured.in.Law.SDTV.x264-XAiO

So this is my second TV rip ever. If there are any problems please tell me. I'm eager to fix whatever issues may arise. I've went through and removed the black bars and resized it to fit the previous Stossel releases. (Thanks skJGZV6z)

Anyway, I ripped this using some cheap Diamond dongle. Ripped using EZ Ripper to their "DVD standard". Then cut into parts to remove commercials using AVIDemux and then join those files. Using that same tool I then convert using MPEG4 AVC (x264) & AAC (Faac) with a file limitation of 350mb, remove the black bars, and resize the video to fit previous Stossel releases. (Thanks skJGZV6z)
